{NORTH has a Limit Raise hand but after WEST's overcall a 3

♥

bid

by NORTH would be preemptive, not inviting. Instead he makes a Support Cue-bid.

SOUTH has just enough that she can bid 4

♥

, knowing that if NORTH has

a real block-buster he will bid on.

NORTH doesn't have a real block-buster.}
